WEBVTT

NOTE Skit starts at anchor #5 with street interviews.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.000
[action] Cut to vox pops.

00:00:02.000 --> 00:00:07.000
[stage direction] (standing in water) I would put a tax on all people who stand in water ... Oh!

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:11.000
<v Man In Bowler Hat>
To boost the British economy I'd tax all foreigners living abroad.

00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:16.000
<v Man In Suit>
I would tax the nude in my bed. No - not tax. What is the word? Oh - 'welcome'.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:20.000
<v It's Man>
I would tax Racquel Welch. I've a feeling she'd tax me.

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:22.500
<v First Business Man>
Bring back hanging and go into rope.

00:00:22.500 --> 00:00:27.000
<v Second Business Man>
I would cut off the more disreputable parts of the body and use the space for playing fields.

00:00:27.000 --> 00:00:29.500
<v Man In Cap>
I would tax holiday snaps.

